{"tha-ap420:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap420:0.2":"Bhaddalivagga ","tha-ap420:0.3":"Yagudayakattheraapadana ","tha-ap420:1.1":"“Atithim me gahetvana, ","tha-ap420:1.2":"agacchim gamakam tada; ","tha-ap420:1.3":"Sampunnanadikam disva, ","tha-ap420:1.4":"sangharamam upagamim. ","tha-ap420:2.1":"Arannaka dhutadhara, ","tha-ap420:2.2":"jhayino lukhacivara; ","tha-ap420:2.3":"Vivekabhirata dhira, ","tha-ap420:2.4":"sangharame vasanti te. ","tha-ap420:3.1":"Gati tesam upacchinna, ","tha-ap420:3.2":"suvimuttana tadinam; ","tha-ap420:3.3":"Pindaya te na gacchanti, ","tha-ap420:3.4":"oruddhanaditaya hi. ","tha-ap420:4.1":"Pasannacitto sumano, ","tha-ap420:4.2":"vedajato katanjali; ","tha-ap420:4.3":"Tandulam me gahetvana, ","tha-ap420:4.4":"yagudanam adasaham. ","tha-ap420:5.1":"Pancannam yagum datvana, ","tha-ap420:5.2":"pasanno sehi panibhi; ","tha-ap420:5.3":"Sakakammabhiraddhoham, ","tha-ap420:5.4":"tavatimsamagacchaham. ","tha-ap420:6.1":"Manimayanca me byamham, ","tha-ap420:6.2":"nibbatti tidase gane; ","tha-ap420:6.3":"Nariganehi sahito, ","tha-ap420:6.4":"modami byamhamuttame. ","tha-ap420:7.1":"Tettimsakkhattum devindo, ","tha-ap420:7.2":"devarajjamakarayim; ","tha-ap420:7.3":"Timsakkhattum cakkavatti, ","tha-ap420:7.4":"maharajjamakarayim. ","tha-ap420:8.1":"Padesarajjam vipulam, ","tha-ap420:8.2":"gananato asankhiyam; ","tha-ap420:8.3":"Devaloke manusse va, ","tha-ap420:8.4":"anubhotva sayam aham. ","tha-ap420:9.1":"Pacchime bhave sampatte, ","tha-ap420:9.2":"pabbajim anagariyam; ","tha-ap420:9.3":"Saha oropite kese, ","tha-ap420:9.4":"sabbam sampativijjhaham. ","tha-ap420:10.1":"Khayato vayato capi, ","tha-ap420:10.2":"sammasanto kalevaram; ","tha-ap420:10.3":"Pure sikkhapadadana, ","tha-ap420:10.4":"arahattamapapunim. ","tha-ap420:11.1":"Sudinnam me danavaram, ","tha-ap420:11.2":"vanijjam sampayojitam; ","tha-ap420:11.3":"Teneva yagudanena, ","tha-ap420:11.4":"pattomhi acalam padam. ","tha-ap420:12.1":"Sokam pariddavam byadhim, ","tha-ap420:12.2":"daratham cittatapanam; ","tha-ap420:12.3":"Nabhijanami uppannam, ","tha-ap420:12.4":"yagudanassidam phalam. ","tha-ap420:13.1":"Yagum sanghassa datvana, ","tha-ap420:13.2":"punnakkhette anuttare; ","tha-ap420:13.3":"Pancanisamse anubhomi, ","tha-ap420:13.4":"aho yagusuyitthata. ","tha-ap420:14.1":"Abyadhita rupavata, ","tha-ap420:14.2":"khippam dhammanisantita; ","tha-ap420:14.3":"Labhita annapanassa, ","tha-ap420:14.4":"ayu pancamakam mama. ","tha-ap420:15.1":"Yo koci vedam janayam, ","tha-ap420:15.2":"sanghe yagum dadeyya so; ","tha-ap420:15.3":"Imani panca thanani, ","tha-ap420:15.4":"patiganheyya pandito. ","tha-ap420:16.1":"Karaniyam katam sabbam, ","tha-ap420:16.2":"bhava ugghatita maya; ","tha-ap420:16.3":"Sabbasava parikkhina, ","tha-ap420:16.4":"natthi dani punabbhavo. ","tha-ap420:17.1":"So aham vicarissami, ","tha-ap420:17.2":"gama gamam pura puram; ","tha-ap420:17.3":"Namassamano sambuddham, ","tha-ap420:17.4":"dhammassa ca sudhammatam. ","tha-ap420:18.1":"Timsakappasahassamhi, ","tha-ap420:18.2":"yam danamadadim tada; ","tha-ap420:18.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap420:18.4":"yagudanassidam phalam. ","tha-ap420:19.1":"Kilesa jhapita mayham, ","tha-ap420:19.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap420:19.3":"viharami anasavo. ","tha-ap420:20.1":"Svagatam vata me asi, ","tha-ap420:20.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap420:20.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam. ","tha-ap420:21.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap420:21.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap420:21.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap420:22.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma yagudayako thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap420:23.1":"Yagudayakattherassapadanam atthamam. "}